{"tid":1516722,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"你地記唔記得有義士被還押? 你寫咗信比佢未?","createTime":"2019-08-29T16:07:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-30T10:25:48.000Z","uid":158090,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"cebbbf8b01deff84980555c39620fded24cbfbb0","tid":1516722,"uid":158090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T16:07:03.000Z","msg":"【星火送暖&mdash;為還押義士打氣】<br />\n<br />\n涉嫌在機場與環球時報「記者」發生衝突、只有19歲的賴雲龍，因同時涉嫌在7月沙田遊行中襲警，現被法庭判處還押候審，等候<span style=\"color: red;\">10月份再次出庭應訊</span>。<br />\n<br />\n就如眾多這一代的年輕人一樣，<span style=\"color: red;\">雲龍因着對香港的愛，在反修例運動中不怕艱辛和困難，冒着被濫捕濫告和被血腥虐殺的風險，不只一次走上前線</span>。雖然在<span style=\"color: red;\">上月已被捕，但無阻他繼續為港爭取撤回反送中條例的決心</span>，結果最終不幸再次被捕更竟要被即時還押。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">面對孤單且突然完全失去自由的日子</span>，在得到他的同意下，星火同盟現邀請大家<span style=\"color: red;\">寫信或心意卡給雲龍</span>，並寄到本平台：九龍尖沙咀郵箱98697號。<br />\n<br />\n各位同道給予雲龍的每一個鼓勵和打氣，<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">能讓他知道自己的戰友從沒有把他遺忘</span></span></strong>。同道們的一字一句，將成為雲龍面對四面圍牆時重要的精神支柱。"},{"pid":"f1dc6f7254abf0ebbb7c158eb1bcc29dc1199357","tid":1516722,"uid":98926,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T16:08:46.000Z","msg":"831遊行<br />\n831死線<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/npq7Ds0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fnpq7Ds0.jpg&h=cd008a46&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VggiLqD.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVggiLqD.gif&h=29ffb828&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VggiLqD.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVggiLqD.gif&h=29ffb828&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VggiLqD.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVggiLqD.gif&h=29ffb828&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VggiLqD.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVggiLqD.gif&h=29ffb828&